297
00:21:38,430 --> 00:21:39,798
{\an8}You don't know?

298
00:21:39,865 --> 00:21:40,699
{\an8}<i>Kota.</i>

299
00:21:42,367 --> 00:21:43,201
{\an8}<i>Kai.</i>

300
