318
00:22:35,854 --> 00:22:40,926
<i>Why does Kato do this alone
without asking the other members?</i>

319
00:22:41,760 --> 00:22:43,729
It's partly because it's faster this way.

320
00:22:43,795 --> 00:22:46,798
There's no time to really explain
what tone I want them to use.

321
00:22:47,432 --> 00:22:50,102
The members have no idea
how much work this is.

322
00:22:50,702 --> 00:22:52,671
They'd be surprised to see me doing this.

323
00:22:53,205 --> 00:22:56,541
They aren't aware of all I do.
I'd say 70% of the work I do

324
00:22:57,609 --> 00:23:00,078
